All codes are derived from source originally written by
Mat Buckland (fup@ai-junkie.com)
for his book
...............................
Programming Game AI by Example 
(September 30, 2004  | ISBN-10: 1556220782  | ISBN-13: 978-1556220784  | Edition: 1)
................................

You can buy the book here:
http://www.amazon.com/Programming-Game-Example-Mat-Buckland/dp/1556220782
Mat Buckland
or (and you can get the original code) at this location:
http://www.jblearning.com/Catalog/9781556220784/student/

I recommend you this book!

